query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(lt mi ml t mc) NoMergeJoin(lt mc mi ml t cn) NoMergeJoin(cn lt mc mi ml t ct) NoMergeJoin(cn ct lt mc mi ml t mk) NoMergeJoin(cn ct lt mc mi mk ml t k) */ select min(cn.name) AS company_name,
min(lt.link) AS link_type,
min(t.title) AS western_follow_up
from link_type AS lt
inner join movie_link AS ml
on lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND lt.link like '%follow%'
inner join title AS t
on ml.movie_id = t.id AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1950 AND 2000
inner join movie_info AS mi
on ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = t.id AND mi.info IN ('Sweden',
'Norway',
'Germany',
'Denmark',
'Swedish',
'Denish',
'Norwegian',
'German')
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.note IS NULL
inner join company_name AS cn
on mc.company_id = cn.id AND cn.country_code <> '[pl]' AND ( cn.name like '%Film%' OR cn.name like '%Warner%')
inner join company_type AS ct
on mc.company_type_id = ct.id AND ct.kind = 'production companies'
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
inner join keyword AS k
on mk.keyword_id = k.id AND k.keyword = 'sequel';
